Given I am viewing an opportunity in "Qualified" stage
And I am the assigned owner
When I click "Send Proposal" and upload the PDF
Then the system moves the opportunity to "Proposal Sent"
And sets the sent_date to current timestamp
And sends notification to the client
And logs the transition in the audit trail

Given I am viewing an opportunity owned by another rep
When I attempt to change the stage
Then I receive "Permission Denied" error
And the stage remains unchanged